    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "祭典への出演が決まってしばらく経った頃",
      "startTime": 2.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのに付き合ってもらってすみません",
      "startTime": 5.3666666943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。それに、最近はあまり\nゆっくり話せてなかったしな",
      "startTime": 11.9333333412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2310887295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nそれで、相談なんですけど",
      "startTime": 16.4977553962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.3310882209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピとの合同練習に……集中出来ないんです",
      "startTime": 19.3310882209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7310886024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピがBIG4になってから、月ストとの差が\n開いていってる気がするんです",
      "startTime": 26.9977552691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達も頑張ってるんですけど\nサニピは仕事の幅がどんどん広がっていて",
      "startTime": 31.7644213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.9644207913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "「月ストに比べてサニピは絶好調」っていう風に\n世間でも思われてるんだと……肌で感じるんです",
      "startTime": 38.5977541247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.564420537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "周りの意見は気にしなくていい……と言いたいけど\n実際は難しいよな",
      "startTime": 48.2333344856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーとして月ストをうまく引っ張れなくて\nこんな風に思われてるのが悔しくて……",
      "startTime": 54.7171868601,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}